description: BMO Short-Term US IG Corporate Bond Hedged to CAD Index ETF has been designed to replicate, to the extent possible, the performance of the Bloomberg U.S. Investment Grade 1-5 Year Corporate Bond CAD Hedged Index, net of expenses. The U.S. dollar currency exposure is hedged back to Canadian dollars.
name: BMO Short-Term US IG Corporate Bond Hedged to CAD Index ETF
